  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Then, for some moments, there was silence. “Well, Daisy Miller,” said the elder lady, presently, “I shouldn’t think you’d want to talk against your own brother!”"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "“Well, he IS tiresome, Mother,” said Daisy, quite without the asperity of a retort."
  },
  {
