  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "“Well!” ejaculated the elder lady again."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "“You haven’t spoken to me for half an hour,” her daughter went on."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
