  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "“Well,” said Winterbourne, “when you deal with natives you must go by the custom of the place. Flirting is a purely American custom; it doesn’t exist here. So when you show yourself in public with Mr. Giovanelli, and without your mother—”"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
